{"tid":306521,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"【一齊練寫字!】連登筆友計劃 (七)","createTime":"2017-07-02T15:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T07:00:30.000Z","uid":53244,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b8f2a95f188342a06dc8cb6bc3dd49d6b9260a2c","tid":306521,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:07:33.000Z","msg":"Hello, 好感謝咁多巴絲支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次筆友PO會交畀絲打<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>好撚急屎</strong></span>做配對, <br />\n絲打好有心機, 大家可以放心參加 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">交表前記得睇左呢度先!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 每個email只可以交表 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1</span></span></strong> 次<br />\n(筆友唔啱你可以email我, 會再配俾你, 唔洗玩分身, 見者即block)<br />\n<br />\n2. 每人獲配<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">一巴一絲</span></span></strong> + <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">Greeting Question </span></span></strong>既email 一封;<br />\n而同時Admin會將你地分配俾其他巴絲打, 所以會有其他人主動Approach既情況出現, 各位唔需要大驚少怪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>例: 假設A係其一參加人，佢會收到B、C嘅資料做佢嘅筆友（一巴一絲），而A嘅資料亦都會send去D到做另一個配對。</strong></span></em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第7回表格:<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/BIyTRkX4CKIgpYp92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FBIyTRkX4CKIgpYp92&d=jw9QCSJXcqqJb5KtwdpFc8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=42f13faa\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/BIyTRkX4CKIgpYp92</a>"},{"pid":"bacbed869c33b5979402b9253bf99d45771ac9d9","tid":306521,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:08:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">截Form時間:<br />\n7 月 8 日 (六), 晚上 11時正</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4300b3bc530d801e551a9172a09e1cf37e1c2191","tid":306521,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:10:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">筆友須知:</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\ni) 大家收到配對後, 可以email同對方簡單介紹下自己,<br />\n然後問下人想寄信 / 收信先, 其他可以留返係信裡面講   <br />\n<br />\nii) 如果巴絲收到完全無上文下理、 九唔搭八既回覆都可以report返俾<span style=\"color: red;\">好撚急屎</span>絲打知.<br />\n<br />\niii) 上幾次都有好多人參加完但唔回信, 個堆email已record, 亦會較少分配俾各有心寫信既巴絲, 無謂浪費大家時間.<br />\n<br />\n要講都講哂, 祝大家書信快樂!  <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0QKqK2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0QKqK2c.jpg&h=aa4ac7fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd7b0d046917d58caad513947acd65306bf231c6","tid":306521,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:12:53.000Z","msg":"Thanks巴打！"},{"pid":"9a9149677d840347d83aa33b987dba78ee3d99ee","tid":306521,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace0796ce7962c7415014c5d757a24ce70f6b48a","tid":306521,"uid":10623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea35174d61ed476879735b7207a15ba3df19bf8b","tid":306521,"uid":53244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:23:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n阿星接力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次拜託你了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a9f2447f660a6d5465301722286da25c10c8b